column5: Nice you actually got to land it.  I loose half of them when they hit on Crappie gear.
Nice catch either way! I bet that was a good ol fight on light gear!!!
Awesome, this happened to me at LPB a few years ago.. go it to the hole then cya! gone....

Yeah - Stoked that I got to set it right in the top of his mouth - made the land a possibility!!!  Head shakes on the light rod where a whole lot of fun and stress with every back and forth.  Thanks guys!
you guys rock! keep the reports coming
you guys rock! keep the reports coming X2
you guys rock! keep the reports coming   X2   Thanks guys!!
